SELECT r.period_end_date,
       r.value as automotive_sales,
       r2.value as automotive_leasing
FROM   cybersyn.sec_report_attributes as r join cybersyn.sec_report_attributes as r2
        ON r.period_end_date = r2.period_end_date join cybersyn.sec_cik_index as i
        ON r.cik = i.cik
WHERE  i.company_name = 'TESLA, INC.'
   and r.measure_description = 'Automotive sales'
   and r2.measure_description = 'Automotive leasing'
   and r.statement = 'Income Statement'
   and r2.statement = 'Income Statement'
   and r.covered_qtrs = 1
   and r2.covered_qtrs = 1
ORDER BY r.period_end_date desc limit 1;
